name: SAG3.ai by Virtuals
description: SAG3 agent does comprehensive risk assessment and analysis of any crypto project (so you don't have to). The agent utilises the latest AI models to conduct extensive research and deep analysis of a given crypto project, based on a variety of factors. The goal of the agent is essentially to save you time by compiling everything that you might want to know about a given crypto project and displaying that information to you in an easily accessible and visually appealing way.
